Simple Photo Collage Birth Announcement

Big Deals! Simple Photo Collage Birth Announcement – Birth Announcement Cards Popular Simple Photo Collage Birth Announcement help you save during this period Simple Photo Collage Birth Announcement See more about itSimple photo birth announcement to announce the arrival of your baby to family and friends. Your newborn’s photo fills the front and is overlayed with "she’s here!" "he’s here!" or "I’am here!" in a contemporary script (you can move this text to another area on the card to suit your photo by selecting editing in the design tool). Add his or her name, arrival date and birth stats. On the reverse side, add four additional photos, a "welcomed by" message and the parent’s and sibling’s first names. Price:$2.39
